  <notes>Spec references: FR-5 (line 127), AC-5b (line 129). Hint: if deployed configjson is byte-equivalent to repo JSON, "no divergence" is the legitimate answer. Hint: the spec says PB-016/PB-018/PB-019 are "verified to reference ActionType 52" — this task creates the empirical evidence backing that claim. If verification FAILS for any, escalate to owner — that's a deployment-gap defect worth surfacing.</notes>

